<placeName cert="high">Apollonopolis Magna</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><g type="stauros"/> τὰ διὰ Σευήρου τοῦ <gap extent="12" reason="lost" unit="character"/> γράμματα ἐδεξάμην, καὶ ἐχάρην μαθὼν ἐν αὐτοῖς τὴν αἰσίαν ὑμῶν 

    <lb n="2"/>κατάστασιν· περὶ Χόμος τοῦ οἰκοδό<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μου μετὰ τέσσαρας <num value="4"/></supplied> ἡμέρας πέμπω ὑμῖν αὐτὸν βερέδοις, ἐπειδὴ 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸ τεσσάρων <num value="4"/> ἡμερῶν Παπατάϊς ὁ πραγματευτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὴς</supplied> ἔβρεξεν τὸν πηλόν, ἐφ᾽ ᾡ <choice><corr>ἀνακτίσῃ</corr><sic>ανακτηση</sic></choice> μικρὸν 

    <lb n="4"/>δι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κάσιμον </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> θαυμά</supplied>ζων χάριν αὐτοῦ διότι μικρὸν δικάσιμον 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐσχ<supplied cert="low" reason="lost">ε </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> καὶ μόγις χθὲς ἔβαλεν τῷ Παπατάϊ ἀρχὴν· 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ διὰ τούτου <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>ετὰ Σευήρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ου </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> Θε</supplied>οῦ κελεύοντος, ὡς εἶπον, μετὰ ἄλλας <expan>τέσσαρ<ex cert="high">ας</ex></expan> <num value="4"/> 

    <lb n="7"/>ἡμέρας πέμπω ὑμῖν αὐτὸν. προσκυνῶ τὴν <expan><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θεοφ</supplied>ύλακ<ex cert="high">τον</ex></expan> ὑμῶν ἀδελφικὴν <expan>δεσπο<ex cert="high">τείαν</ex></expan> καὶ δι᾽ ὑμῶν 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="8"/>τὸν <expan>θεοφύλ<ex cert="high">ακτον</ex></expan> καὶ κοινὸν ἀδελφὸν καὶ τὰ κοινὰ τέκνα. <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μέχρι</supplied> δὲ τῆς γραφῆς τῆς παρούσης ἐπιστολῆς 

    <lb n="9"/>οὐκ ἔπεμψα εἰς τὴν <gap extent="25" reason="lost" unit="character"/> μετὰ τοῦ κοινοῦ τέκνου Ἄπα Ἰωάννου, ἀλλὰ καὶ 

    <lb n="10"/>εικ<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> ἀ</supplied>λλὰ καὶ καθαράν· κελεῦσαι δὲ παρακαλῶ 

    <lb n="11"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">  συγ</supplied>χωρήσωσιν ἐπαρθῆναι ἐκ τῶν κοπέντων 

    <lb n="12"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> ἀ</supplied>νῆλθαν κόψαι χθές· μάθῃ οὖν τὸν σκοπὸν ὑμῶν 

    <lb n="13"/>ὁ Ἡρακλείδης καὶ Ποιμένις ὅτι οὐ <choice><corr>συγχωρεῖτε</corr><sic>συγχωρητε</sic></choice> ἀπ᾽ αὐτῶν <g type="stauros"/> <expan>μ<ex cert="high">ηνὶ</ex></expan> Φαῶφι <num value="14">ιδ</num> <g type="stauros"/> <g type="stauros"/> ἰδίοις <expan>μ<ex cert="high">ου</ex></expan> <expan>δεσπό<ex cert="high">ταις</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> </ab></div></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="700" notBefore="651" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 2. Hälfte VII</date></p></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Tag: 11. (12.) Okt. Zur Datierung vgl. BL VIII, S. 10.</p></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Apoll.</title><biblScope type="numbers">64</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">39123</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0061</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">64</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0061;;64" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.39123" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div></body></text></TEI.2>